disclaimer.subtitle: Reviews from past guests help our community learn more about each home. By default, reviews are sorted by recency. Only the guest who booked the reservation can leave a review, and Airbnb only moderates reviews flagged for not following our policies. To be eligible for a percentile ranking or guest favorite label, listings need 5 or more recent reviews. Criteria is subject to change. Learn more in our Help Center

verifiedHelpModalContent.title: How listings are verified
verifiedHelpModalContent.body:
Listings are verified after the Host submits photos or videos to show their place is where they say it is––and they have access to it.

In some cases, a listing can be verified if guest reviews confirm its location, the Host provides extra documents, or if the listing is managed by a company that signs an agreement.

This process has safeguards, but is not a guarantee that every detail on the listing is accurate. Learn about listing verification

section.houseRulesSubtitle: You'll be staying in someone's home, so please treat it with care and respect.

html.htmlText:
Don't make noise after 10pm please.

Parties and events are not allowed​

Smoking inside the apartment is not allowed (electronic cigarette included).​

​The apartment must be returned in the same condition as you found it

If by any chance a plate, glass or anything else is broken during your stay, just let us know (these things can happen)

In short, we do our best to prepare the apartment so you have the best possible stay.

Please make it easier for us to welcome future guests by understanding you in a respectful and responsible manner.
​

reviews.comments:
Super logement propre
Je vous le recommande vivement !

The place was well worth the money in such a good location close to the heart of Paris! All amenities were included, many cafes and supermarkets nearby, and public transport within a 10 min walk radius. I would definitely choose this place again when visiting Paris!
ótimo apartamento: muito espaço,  bem equipado

localizedReview.comments: great apartment: plenty of space,  well-equipped

reviews.comments: You will get all you need in this apartment! Great neighborhood just like a home. Come and you will know what I mean here.

Très beau séjour !
Merci pour l’accueil et la flexibilité

localizedReview.comments:
Very nice stay!
Thank you for the hospitality and flexibility

reviews.comments: Less than 10 minutes walk to Metro and everything was comfortable and pleasant.

Superbe appartement, propre et fidèle aux photos.
Très bien placé.
Un supermarché pas loin. Ligne de métro 7 proche de l’appartement.
Si nous revenons sur Paris nous reviendrons très certainement ici.

localizedReview.comments:
Beautiful apartment, clean and true to the photos.
Very well placed.
A supermarket not far away. Metro line 7 close to the apartment.
If we come back to Paris we will most certainly come back here.

reviews.comments: L’appartement est propre , accessible , fonctionnel . Correspond exactement à l’annonce et des hôtes qui ont su parfaitement nous accueillir ! Je recommande !

localizedReview.comments: The apartment is clean , accessible , functional . Exactly matches the listing and hosts who were able to host us perfectly! I recommend it!

reviews.comments:
Spędziliśmy w mieszkanku osiem dni i było przytulnie jak w domu.
Kuchnia z kompletnym wyposażeniem, łazienka z prysznicem, bez wanny,
tak jak lubimy. Wygodne łóżka, czysta pościel, no i po całym dniu podróżowania po Paryżu, komfortowy odpoczynek przed telewizorem z Netflix'em. W bezpośrednim sąsiedztwie malutka Pizzeria z bardzo dobrą ofertą, dodatkowo sklep ze wszystkim, warzywa, owoce, wina, artykuły kuchenne. Całkiem blisko stacja Metro stacja Pierre et Marie Curie linii nr 7
Polecamy to miejsce
Alicia Sabrina Lech

localizedReview.comments:
We spent eight days in the apartment and it was cozy like home.
Fully equipped kitchen, bathroom with shower, no bathtub,
as we like. Comfortable beds, clean linens, and after a day of traveling in Paris, a comfortable rest in front of the TV with Netflix. In the immediate vicinity of a tiny Pizzeria with a very good offer, in addition, a shop with everything, vegetables, fruits, wines, cooking utensils. Pretty close to Metro station Pierre et Marie Curie line 7
We recommend this place
Alicia Sabrina Lech

reviews.comments:
All good !
I want to give you some advice (for the owner) .... I noticed that you don't deal directly with this business...
Experienced people must be involved for this business! ... if you don't have time to manage the business...
In general, everything was ok...
I recommend staying in this location when you want to visit Paris...
But ... Maybe I'm too picky...🤣
Cleanliness ok, quietness ok, comfort ok, facilities ok, ...communication needs to be improved..., please...👍
, 8 minutes to Metro Pierre & Marie Curie...
P.S.
...You see that the coffee caps for the Bosch automatic are not compatible with your model...
Auchan is not far ...
The one who bought them coffee caps...bought caps for another model of coffee machine..
All in all I will come back here ... 👍😊 ... maybe the host will gain more experience in managing Airbnb accommodations ...
Thank you ... 😘
It was a wonderful stay...
My overall grade... 9.19....😉

très bon séjour avec tous les commodités,proche des stations métro
appartement propre et ressemble à 100% aux photos.
je recommande

localizedReview.comments:
very good stay with all amenities,close to metro stations
clean apartment and looks 100% like photos.
i recommend it

reviews.comments: Easy communication and overall a great stay with close access Metro and into Paris
Great little place a quick walk from the M7.

Very nice and comfortable apartment, very clean. Wifi and smart tv enabled spending evenings watching movies. The host was very nice, helpful and responsive, reacted immediately when a small problem with pipes occured and provided a lot of information in advance.  The only thing missing from the description was the microwave oven.

Anfitrião super receptivo, apartamento extremamente limpo e organizado, localização super tranquilo para quem gosta de silencio, tem mercado no final da rua e cafeteria, voltaria a ficar novamente na acomodacao. Recomendo !

localizedReview.comments: Super receptive host, extremely clean and organized apartment, super quiet location for those who like to be quiet, have a market at the end of the street and cafeteria, it would be back in the room again. I recommend it!

reviews.comments:
The apartment was clean. convenient, near to tram,bus and 10 minutes to the metro.
We really enjoyed our stay. I was able to cook some meals.
The only thing is that there is no microwave by itself.
The hosts are very easy to communicate with. Instructions were very clear.
Thank you!

L'appartamento è molto bello, luminoso come nelle foto che non capita mai. All'interno c'è tutto per abitare. Noi siamo stati una settimana con bambini e dovevamo cucinare per loro, sono allergici ai cibi perciò abbiamo trovato tutte le stoviglie per cucinare. La posizione della casa per noi era confortevole anche perchè avevamo una macchina a noleggio perciò per parcheggiare costava poco 4 euro al giorno invece in centro costa 4 -6 euro all'ora. Vicino la casa trovate il supermercato, frutta e verdura, pasticcierie e pizzeria. La metropolitana è a 15 min a piedi.
Consiglio al 100% e sicuramente tornerei volentieri
Grazie

localizedReview.comments:
The apartment is very nice, bright as in the photos that never happen. Inside there is everything to live in. We stayed with children for a week and we had to cook for them, they are allergic to food so we found all the dishes for cooking. The location of the house was also comfortable for us because we had a rental car so to park it cost little 4 euros per day instead in the center it costs 4 -6 euros per hour. Near the house you can find the supermarket, fruits and vegetables, pastry shops and pizzeria. The subway is a 15-minute walk away.
I recommend 100% and would definitely be happy to come back
Thank you

reviews.comments: velmi krásné ubytování v klidné části Paříže. Metro i tram dostupné do 10min. Být velmi dobře vybavený.. krásně jsme si upekli pizzu, ohřáli jídlo i ranní křupavé toasty. Jediné co chybělo..bylo prkénko na krájení zeleniny nebo masa.  Vše prostě bylo perfektní a velice děkuji hostiteli za krásný týden v klidu a pohodě. Zdraví Jana s rodinou z České republiky

localizedReview.comments: very beautiful accommodation in a quiet part of Paris. Metro and tram can be reached within 10min. Being very well equipped.. we baked a lovely pizza, warmed the food and the morning crunchy toast. The only thing missing...was a cutting board for cutting vegetables or meat.  Everything was just perfect and thank you very much to the host for a wonderful week in peace and quiet. Jana and family from the Czech Republic

reviews.comments: 모든 것이 완벽했습니다! 추천드려요:)

localizedReview.comments: Everything was perfect! I recommend it:)

reviews.comments:
Logement très confort, Calme, Lumineux et Spacieux.
Emplacement proche de Métro, Magasins, et centre du paris.
L'appartement est équipé avec tout le nécessaire (Cuisine, salle de bain, chambre) et bien isolé
Lit très confortable et les photos sont fidèles à la réalité.
Fabrice était très accueillant et responsable et surtout réactif.
Je vous remercie pour votre professionnalisme.

localizedReview.comments:
Very comfortable, quiet, bright and spacious accommodation.
Location close to Metro, Shops, and center of Paris.
The apartment is equipped with all the necessities (Kitchen, bathroom, bedroom) and well insulated
Very comfortable bed and the photos are accurate.
Fabrice was very friendly and responsible and above all responsive.
I appreciate it for your professionalism.

reviews.comments: assez bien à tous égards.

Our stay was delightful, the apparent is situated in a calm area about 10-15 minutes away from the metro station.
The accommodations were as described, the apartment was clean upon our arrival and the beds very comfortable.
A convenience store is only few meters away and a bit further a small mall.
The host is very responsive and friendly.
it is a bit far from the centre but definitely worth it, great apartment well equipped, I would stay again and recommend it .

Tout simplement excellent! Tres bel et chic appartement qui a rempli toutes ses promesses. Le contenu est conforme à la description et aux photos. Toutes les commodités y sont pour un sejour agreable. J'ai particulièrement apprécié la convivialité des lieux. L'environnement est sécurisé et paisible, le calme y regne: propice pour le repos loin du vacarme du centre ville de Paris.
L'appartement est à sept minutes de la station de métro et le super marché au bout de la rue. On y trouve d'autres commodités qui rendent l'environnement plaisant: restaurants, fats food, boulangerie pâtisserie...
Fabrice est un hotte accessible et à l'écoute. Une flexibilité remarquable par rapport aux heures d'arrivée et départ.
J'y reviendrais volontiers...

localizedReview.comments:
Simply excellent! Very nice and chic apartment that has fulfilled all its promises. Content is as described and photos. All the amenities are for a pleasant stay. I particularly appreciated the conviviality of the place. The environment is secure and peaceful, the calm reigns: conducive to rest away from the noise of downtown Paris.
The apartment is seven minutes from the subway station and the super market at the end of the street. There are other amenities that make the environment pleasant: restaurants, fats food, bakery pastry...
Fabrice is an accessible and attentive range hood. Remarkable flexibility with check-in and checkout times.
I'd be happy to come back...
